sources.title: Teenage Devil Dolls (1955) GRINDHOUSE
sources.description:
Stars: Barbara Marks, Kurt Martell, Robert A. Sherry 
 Director: Bamlet Lawrence Price Jr.

 Cassandra falls in with the wrong crowd in high school. Her home life is not great, and she turns to a group of delinquent bikers to help escape. Before long she's doing drugs and failing her classes until she has no chance of getting in to college. She marries her clueless high school sweetheart, but soon grows desperate for more drugs and falls into her old habits!
